node.text:
Kicking my first soccer ball in Hershey. Winning my first professional trophy in Berlin. Scoring my first USMNT goal in Kansas City. Winning the Champions League in Porto. Captaining & lifting my first USMNT trophy in Denver.

Now it’s time to start a new chapter and create new memories. 

Today I’m joining a new family, the #PUMAFam and together we are going to inspire the next generation of players out there. @pumafootball
